<h2 class="bold font-l">The Death of Stalin</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Field Marshal Zhukov announces that he doesn't intend to die of thirst during Stalin's funeral. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/IncomingHam" class='trope-example-link'>Incoming Ham</a></p>
